BUTTONROLE_ADVANCED_DESCRIPTION:
Click the buttons below to add/remove a button

Make sure to follow the requirements below:
`- ` A label can be any text or `none`
`- ` An emoji can be any emoji, an ID or `none`
`- ` The style being `PRIMARY`, `SECONDARY`, `SUCCESS` or `DANGER`
`- ` The mode being `TOGGLE`, `ADD` or `REMOVE`
`- ` Required role being a role the member needs

You can see a select-menu below with the buttons you already set up
BUTTONROLE_ADVANCED_ROLE_REMOVE_RESOLVER: Select the button you want to remove
BUTTONROLE_ADVANCED_ROLES_PLACEHOLDER:
Up to 5 roles divided with a ','
Attach required role with '|'
BUTTONROLES_ADVANCED_ROLES_INSTRUCTION:
Please send the next messages with the following format:
```md
@{0} <role> <mode> <style> <emoji> <label>
<required role>```
`- ` [The style must be a number between 1 and 4](https://discord.com/assets/7bb017ce52cfd6575e21c058feb3883b.png)
​ ​ ​ ​ ​`- ` **{1}**: Primary
​ ​ ​ ​ ​`- ` **{2}**: Secondary
​ ​ ​ ​ ​`- ` **{3}**: Success
​ ​ ​ ​ ​`- ` **{4}**: Destructive
`- ` The mode must be a one of the following
​ ​ ​ ​ ​`- ` **toggle**: Allows adding and removing
​ ​ ​ ​ ​`- ` **add**: Allows only adding
​ ​ ​ ​ ​`- ` **remove**: Allows only removing
`- ` A label **or** emoji must be provided
`- ` A label can be any text less than 100 characters or none
`- ` An emoji can be any emoji, `default` or `none`
`- ` Maximum 25 roles
`- ` There must be a newline before the required role
`- ` The role required to use the button
Send `done` to finish or `cancel` to cancel
